Class ProjectData

java.lang.Object
ProjectData
public class ProjectData extends Object
This class is used to create the ProjectData object that stores information that can be accessed or modified

  • Constructor Summary

    Constructors
    Constructor
    Description
    ProjectData()
    Array constructor
    Creates a two-arraylist object, the first which contains all existing projects and the second for complete projects which are removed from the first array once the program is terminated.
